Package org.dspace.sword2

Interface SwordContentIngester

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractSwordContentIngester, BinaryContentIngester, SimpleZipContentIngester, SwordMETSContentIngester
    public interface SwordContentIngester
    Interface behind which can be implemented ingest mechanisms for SWORD deposit requests. Instances of this class should be obtained via the SwordIngesterFactory class.
    Author:
    Richard Jones

        Ingest the package as described in the given Deposit object within the given DSpace Context
        Parameters:
        context - The relevant DSpace Context.
        deposit - the original deposit request
        target - target DSpace object
        verboseDescription - The description.
        Returns:
        the result of the deposit
        Throws:
        DSpaceSwordException - can be thrown by the internals of the DSpace SWORD implementation
        org.swordapp.server.SwordError - SWORD error per SWORD spec
        org.swordapp.server.SwordAuthException - thrown if unable to authenticate
        org.swordapp.server.SwordServerException - thrown by SWORD server implementation
